  "about": "Class seat number: 28\n\nA transfer student who aims to kill Koro-sensei. He is brought in along with his guardian, Shiro. Itona claims to be the younger brother of Koro-sensei, however, he does not appear to be related by blood. Their only similarity being that Itona can create tentacles from his hair that are much like Koro-sensei's. Itona is obsessed with power and aims to be much more powerful than he currently is.",
